01:29:39.731 --> 01:29:40.959
Wilson, you're up.

01:29:41.032 --> 01:29:42.056
Yeah, over here.

01:29:42.133 --> 01:29:44.124
Listen, what's the first thing
you're gonna do

01:29:44.202 --> 01:29:45.260
if you make world champion?

01:29:46.104 --> 01:29:49.870
First thing, I'm gonna have
to go and buy some turtles.

01:29:50.008 --> 01:29:51.236
What's that? Turtles?

01:29:51.309 --> 01:29:52.742
Yeah, well,
I said to the kids when

01:29:52.811 --> 01:29:54.278
I was leaving the house
this morning

01:29:54.346 --> 01:29:55.938
that I was gonna
bring back the title

01:29:56.014 --> 01:29:57.811
and they thought
I said "turtle. "

01:29:59.517 --> 01:30:00.541
Yeah.

01:30:00.618 --> 01:30:02.313
So naturally,
I don't want to let them down.

01:30:02.387 --> 01:30:04.480
But if I could bring home
the title and a turtle

01:30:04.556 --> 01:30:06.456
they sure would be tickled.

01:30:06.524 --> 01:30:08.651
You got that?
"Title, turtle," right?

01:30:08.727 --> 01:30:11.525
<i>Jake Greenblatt
from Chicago Trib.</i>

01:30:12.330 --> 01:30:14.161
Hello, Jake.
