01:30:14.232 --> 01:30:15.529
What's changed, Jimmy?

01:30:15.600 --> 01:30:18.626
I mean, you couldn't win a
fight for love or money, right?

01:30:18.703 --> 01:30:20.728
How do you explain
your comeback?

01:30:20.972 --> 01:30:22.439
Well, you
know, the truth is, Jake

01:30:22.507 --> 01:30:24.941
for a number of years there
we was fighting injured.

01:30:25.677 --> 01:30:28.737
I broke my hand
more than once.

01:30:29.647 --> 01:30:32.138
I got in a car accident one
time, we was on the road

01:30:32.217 --> 01:30:34.515
and I had to get that fixed.

01:30:35.320 --> 01:30:37.288
I had a run of bad luck.

01:30:39.624 --> 01:30:42.787
And, this time around,
I know what I'm fighting for.

01:30:42.861 --> 01:30:44.886
Yeah? What's that, Jimmy?

01:30:45.897 --> 01:30:46.989
Milk.

01:30:47.165 --> 01:30:48.291
Milk?

01:30:49.067 --> 01:30:51.035
<i>Sporty Lewis,
New York Herald.</i>

01:30:51.436 --> 01:30:52.596
Sporty.

01:30:52.804 --> 01:30:54.601
Actually, my question's
for Mrs. Braddock.

01:30:55.373 --> 01:30:58.433
Mrs. Braddock, my readers
would love to know

01:30:58.643 --> 01:31:00.941
how do you feel
about the fact that

01:31:01.346 --> 01:31:03.109
Max Baer's killed two men
in the ring?

01:31:04.549 --> 01:31:06.346
So how do you feel
about that, ma'am?

01:31:06.951 --> 01:31:08.851
Are you scared
for your husband's life?

01:31:08.920 --> 01:31:11.787
She's scared for Max Baer, is
who she's scared for, Mr. Lewis.

01:31:11.856 --> 01:31:14.950
Okay, how about
one more question, folks?

01:31:25.970 --> 01:31:27.528
