Joe, Jim, come on in.
Have a seat.

01:31:31.342 --> 01:31:32.707
Right here.

01:31:35.113 --> 01:31:37.138
Editorial says
this fight is good as murder.

01:31:38.650 --> 01:31:41.414
And everybody associated with
it should be hauled into court

01:31:41.486 --> 01:31:43.078
and prosecuted afterwards.

01:31:43.154 --> 01:31:45.281
They say the paper's getting
all sorts of letters

01:31:45.356 --> 01:31:47.221
from people saying
you're their inspiration.

01:31:47.292 --> 01:31:49.021
Like you saved their lives
or something.

01:31:49.094 --> 01:31:51.062
If you ask me,
it's a lot of crap.

01:31:51.429 --> 01:31:53.090
But if I'm gonna
promote this fight

01:31:53.164 --> 01:31:55.826
I'm not getting hung out to
dry if something happens to you.

01:31:55.900 --> 01:31:57.231
You're all heart.

01:31:58.369 --> 01:31:59.802
My heart's for my family, Joe.

01:31:59.871 --> 01:32:01.463
My brains and my balls
are for business

01:32:01.539 --> 01:32:02.528
and this is business.

01:32:02.607 --> 01:32:04.404
You got me?
Gotcha.

01:32:08.646 --> 01:32:11.240
You will know exactly
what you're up against.

01:32:12.450 --> 01:32:13.917
And my attorney,
Mr. Mills

01:32:13.985 --> 01:32:17.045
will witness that I've done
everything in my power to warn you.

01:32:20.391 --> 01:32:22.359
You know,
I seen the Carnera fight.

01:32:23.261 --> 01:32:24.888
Carnera's height saved him.

01:32:24.963 --> 01:32:26.760
He was knocked down 12 times.

01:32:26.831 --> 01:32:29.561
Exactly. Would've been worse
if he was shorter.

01:32:29.634 --> 01:32:32.603
Baer had to punch up to hit
him. Took a little something off.

01:32:41.579 --> 01:32:43.171
That's Frankie Campbell.

01:32:43.815 --> 01:32:45.976
Stand-up fighter,
knows how to take a punch.

01:32:47.785 --> 01:32:49.377
His style familiar, Jim?

01:32:50.855 --> 01:32:54.484
Like looking in a mirror, huh?
Hey, he don't need to see this.

01:32:54.559 --> 01:32:56.322
He'll see it
or I'll call off the fight.

01:33:08.006 --> 01:33:09.974
You see that combination?

01:33:10.041 --> 01:33:11.736
Campbell didn't go down
on the first punch.

01:33:11.809 --> 01:33:13.572
He was a tough guy.

01:33:14.379 --> 01:33:17.348
Second one killed him
on the spot.

01:33:24.255 --> 01:33:26.553
