We'll snap some pics
on your way out.

01:36:13.224 --> 01:36:14.623
If you change your
mind tomorrow

01:36:14.692 --> 01:36:16.421
at least we got some
good press out of it.

01:36:16.494 --> 01:36:18.359
Good. Come on.

01:36:30.375 --> 01:36:32.240
It's gorgeous!

01:36:33.911 --> 01:36:36.106
Jimmy, can we get silver
faucets? Of course.

01:36:36.180 --> 01:36:38.171
How many you
want? A dozen? Right.

