Oh, that's nice.
Yeah.

01:36:51.763 --> 01:36:54.197
Sporty Lewis wrote that.
Sporty Lewis?

01:36:55.433 --> 01:36:56.957
Yeah. And get this.

01:36:57.301 --> 01:36:59.030
"In a land that's
downtrodden

01:36:59.103 --> 01:37:02.834
"Braddock's comeback is
giving hope to every American.

01:37:04.475 --> 01:37:06.670
"People who were ready
to throw in the towel

01:37:06.744 --> 01:37:10.180
"are finding inspiration in
their new hero, Jim Braddock.

01:37:10.815 --> 01:37:13.215
"As Damon Runyon
has already written

01:37:13.284 --> 01:37:16.742
he's truly
the Cinderella Man. "

01:37:17.588 --> 01:37:19.249
Cinderella Man?
Yeah.

01:37:19.323 --> 01:37:23.191
Oh, I like it. It's kind of
girly. Yeah, kind of. Yeah.

01:37:23.261 --> 01:37:25.627
Oh, brother.
Yeah, this is gonna be fun.

01:37:25.897 --> 01:37:27.762
Excuse me.
Jim.

01:37:29.100 --> 01:37:31.967
I'm not quite finished yet.
Beg your pardon, sir.

01:37:32.103 --> 01:37:33.434
Thank you.

01:37:33.905 --> 01:37:36.703
You know what?
I got the bill here. Yeah.

01:37:36.974 --> 01:37:39.966
Johnston. He's a big spender.
He's gonna leave a big, big tip.

01:37:40.044 --> 01:37:41.978
Yeah. He's a real peach.

01:37:42.046 --> 01:37:43.877
Gotta love the guy.
Right, sweetie?

01:37:43.948 --> 01:37:45.711
Look at this.
This is me?

01:37:45.783 --> 01:37:46.772
I know it is.

01:37:50.721 --> 01:37:51.847
Jimmy.

01:38:11.509 --> 01:38:12.601
Oh, boy.

01:38:14.479 --> 01:38:17.846
You think Johnston set that
up? Oh, yeah. I think. Maybe.

01:38:17.915 --> 01:38:20.008
A few extra pics
for the dailies.

01:38:21.452 --> 01:38:23.511
From the gentleman
who just arrived.

01:38:23.588 --> 01:38:26.557
<i>Mr. Baer said
to wish you bon voyage.</i>

01:38:31.262 --> 01:38:33.822
Don't open it. Put it in a
bag. We'll take it with us.

01:38:33.898 --> 01:38:35.456
Hey, Joey?
Yeah?

01:38:35.533 --> 01:38:37.797
Get the coats.
Jim.

01:38:47.411 --> 01:38:49.140
Well,
if it ain't Cinderella Man.

01:38:50.481 --> 01:38:51.971
Thanks for the champagne,
Mr. Baer.

01:38:52.049 --> 01:38:55.212
You're doing a great job publicizing
the fight. I really appreciate it.

01:38:55.286 --> 01:38:58.585
I hope it's gonna be a very
successful night for both of us.

01:38:58.656 --> 01:39:01.147
You keep telling people you're
gonna kill me in the ring.

01:39:02.493 --> 01:39:03.926
I got three kids at home.

01:39:03.995 --> 01:39:06.190
