particularly my wife.

01:39:06.264 --> 01:39:07.788
Listen, Braddock.

01:39:08.566 --> 01:39:11.296
I'm asking you sincerely
not to take this fight.

01:39:11.936 --> 01:39:15.201
Now, you seem like a decent
fellow. People admire you.

01:39:15.573 --> 01:39:16.938
I really don't
want to hurt you.

01:39:18.209 --> 01:39:19.676
It's no joke, pal.

01:39:21.178 --> 01:39:23.339
People die in fairy tales
all the time.

01:39:23.414 --> 01:39:24.904
Hey, Max, how about a picture?

01:39:24.982 --> 01:39:26.244
Hey, Jim! How about a shot?

01:39:26.317 --> 01:39:28.080
There you go. Take it easy. Just smile.

01:39:28.152 --> 01:39:29.483
One more!

01:39:29.687 --> 01:39:32.247
Yeah. I think the smart thing
would be for you to take a fall.

01:39:32.823 --> 01:39:34.950
Circus act's over, old man.

01:39:38.062 --> 01:39:39.689
Right here, Max.
There you go.

01:39:39.764 --> 01:39:42.631
I think I'll go a few rounds
with the dancing Baer.

01:39:42.867 --> 01:39:44.334
Yeah, there you go.

01:39:44.902 --> 01:39:46.961
Come on, Jim.
