ring. How about that, champ?

01:39:52.476 --> 01:39:54.000
Come on. Let's go, Jim.

01:39:54.078 --> 01:39:55.739
Max, my wife, Mae.

01:39:56.314 --> 01:39:57.645
You ought to talk to him, Mae.

01:39:58.482 --> 01:40:00.575
You are far too pretty
to be a widow.

01:40:02.486 --> 01:40:04.477
That's not nice, Max.
Not nice. Come on.

01:40:04.555 --> 01:40:07.319
On second thought, maybe I can
comfort you after he's gone.

01:40:07.391 --> 01:40:10.451
Hey, I said shut your
goddamn mouth, you punk!

01:40:16.233 --> 01:40:18.599
Sorry.
Send me the cleaning bill.

01:40:19.937 --> 01:40:21.404
Get that, boys?

01:40:21.806 --> 01:40:24.104
Now he's got his wife
doing his fighting for him.

01:40:28.679 --> 01:40:30.704
Yeah. Ain't she something?

01:40:35.586 --> 01:40:36.814
All right. Get me a drink.

01:40:48.132 --> 01:40:50.259
All right.
Three-punch combo, okay?

01:40:50.668 --> 01:40:52.863
Pop, pop, bang. Come on.

01:40:55.006 --> 01:40:55.995
Yeah.

01:40:56.073 --> 01:40:57.973
Oh, that's good.
One more time.

01:40:58.042 --> 01:41:00.840
Keep your thumbs tucked in.
Keep your elbows in.

01:41:00.978 --> 01:41:02.878
All right.
That's enough, now.

01:41:02.947 --> 01:41:04.312
There's some sting in that.

01:41:04.382 --> 01:41:05.781
That's enough, please.

01:41:05.850 --> 01:41:07.784
Good. Yeah, that's good. Bang!

01:41:10.287 --> 01:41:12.016
I want a turn, Dad. All right.

01:41:12.089 --> 01:41:14.353
Hey, where's your defense?
Come on, get your hand up.

01:41:14.425 --> 01:41:15.414
I want a turn.

01:41:17.695 --> 01:41:19.822
Left, right,
left. Pop, pop, bang.

01:41:24.835 --> 01:41:26.496
Come on, Howie.

01:41:28.406 --> 01:41:31.204
All right, that's enough!
No boxing in the house!

01:41:31.475 --> 01:41:33.375
No boxing out of the house.
All right?

01:41:33.444 --> 01:41:35.105
No boxing. Period!

01:41:35.813 --> 01:41:37.303
You're gonna stay in school.

01:41:37.381 --> 01:41:38.609
Then you're gonna go
to college

01:41:38.683 --> 01:41:40.116
and you're gonna have
professions.

01:41:40.184 --> 01:41:43.415
Because you're not gonna have
your skulls smashed in, too!

01:41:43.521 --> 01:41:45.955
Do you understand me?
Is that clear?

01:41:54.699 --> 01:41:57.998
Hey, why don't you boys go and
get ready for bed, all right?

01:42:21.358 --> 01:42:22.985
I used to pray

01:42:24.261 --> 01:42:26.695
for you to get hurt
just enough

01:42:28.032 --> 01:42:30.091
so you couldn't fight anymore.

01:42:30.968 --> 01:42:34.529
And when they took your license
away, even scared as I was

01:42:34.805 --> 01:42:38.104
I went to the church
and I thanked God for it.

01:42:38.909 --> 01:42:40.536
'Cause I always knew

01:42:40.644 --> 01:42:44.102
a day might come
when it could kill you.

01:42:44.682 --> 01:42:47.412
I just knew it, Jimmy.
And now it's here.

01:42:47.485 --> 01:42:49.180
You just got the jitters,
that's all.

01:42:49.253 --> 01:42:52.051
He's killed two men, Jimmy!
What's worth it?

01:42:53.791 --> 01:42:57.659
I have to believe I got some
kind of say over our lives. Okay?

01:42:58.329 --> 01:43:00.854
You know, that if things are
bad, that we can change them

01:43:00.931 --> 01:43:02.899
we can make things better
for our family.

01:43:02.967 --> 01:43:06.403
But I need you to be safe

01:43:06.470 --> 01:43:07.937
Nothing's safe anymore, Mae.
so much.

01:43:08.005 --> 01:43:08.994
And without that

01:43:09.073 --> 01:43:11.303
I need you to be safe!
nothing's safe at all.

01:43:11.375 --> 01:43:12.569
All right.

01:43:12.643 --> 01:43:15.510
I have stood by for all of it.

01:43:16.614 --> 01:43:17.945
Until now.

01:43:19.617 --> 01:43:22.711
Not for this, Jimmy.
I just can't.

01:43:23.621 --> 01:43:25.851
So you train all you want.

01:43:25.923 --> 01:43:28.858
Make a show of it
for yourself, for the papers.

01:43:29.326 --> 01:43:31.692
But you find a way
out of that fight.

01:43:31.829 --> 01:43:34.354
Break your hand again
if you have to.

01:43:50.047 --> 01:43:51.036
Is he all right?

01:43:58.155 --> 01:43:59.713
So, how's he doing?

01:44:00.357 --> 01:44:02.552
He's old. He's arthritic.

01:44:02.827 --> 01:44:05.387
And his ribs haven't been
right since the Lasky fight.

01:44:06.096 --> 01:44:08.087
What's the bad news,
