to Max's head.</i>

02:03:50.413 --> 02:03:52.142
<i>Baer comes swinging across
with a long, swinging</i>

02:03:52.215 --> 02:03:54.206
<i>It's the cops.
right to Braddock's head.</i>

02:03:54.917 --> 02:03:56.475
<i>Braddock stumbles away.</i>

02:03:56.552 --> 02:03:58.417
<i>Baer tries that right again!</i>

02:03:59.155 --> 02:04:02.056
<i>They come together.
Braddock swings a left and a right.</i>

02:04:02.125 --> 02:04:03.217
Please, Ma.

02:04:03.292 --> 02:04:05.317
<i>Max comes back with a left and
a right of his own.</i>

02:04:05.395 --> 02:04:07.829
<i>Braddock sticks out a left!
Baer still after him.</i>

02:04:07.897 --> 02:04:08.955
<i>Another left!</i>

02:04:09.032 --> 02:04:12.160
<i>And a hard right by Braddock
that rocked Baer for a moment!</i>

02:04:12.235 --> 02:04:14.066
<i>Baer tries that right again.</i>

02:04:17.707 --> 02:04:19.072
<i>A hard right
to Braddock's head!</i>

02:04:19.142 --> 02:04:21.872
<i>Braddock is hurt.
His legs are gone.</i>

02:04:29.919 --> 02:04:32.319
<i>Braddock sticks out a left!
Another left!</i>

02:04:37.260 --> 02:04:39.922
<i>Neither man will back down!
It's a slugfest, folks!</i>

02:04:39.996 --> 02:04:41.725
<i>And there's the bell!</i>

02:04:42.932 --> 02:04:45.560
<i>James J. Braddock has exhibited
a lot of heart here</i>

02:04:45.635 --> 02:04:48.263
<i>over 11 grueling rounds
with the champion.</i>

02:04:48.337 --> 02:04:51.670
<i>Nobody expected him to last
more than a few innings with Baer.</i>

02:04:51.741 --> 02:04:54.642
<i>Yet here he is.
And he's held his own.</i>

02:04:55.211 --> 02:04:58.112
<i>But now we head
into the championship rounds, folks.</i>

02:05:00.983 --> 02:05:03.850
Hey, Jim, look at me.

02:05:05.822 --> 02:05:08.985
I swear to God, boy,
win, lose or draw

02:05:09.592 --> 02:05:11.992
Thanks, Joey.
For all of it.

02:05:13.796 --> 02:05:16.697
You son of a bitch.
All right. Stop talking.

02:05:16.766 --> 02:05:18.097
Get in there!

02:05:19.035 --> 02:05:20.559
And bury him!

02:05:20.636 --> 02:05:22.103
Finish him off.

02:05:22.271 --> 02:05:23.704
Come on, Jimmy!

02:05:29.812 --> 02:05:31.871
<i>Here in the 12th,
James J. Braddock</i>

02:05:31.948 --> 02:05:34.712
<i>is showing this crowd
what heart is all about.</i>

02:05:42.191 --> 02:05:44.056
<i>Jimmy seems to be
timing that left</i>

02:05:44.127 --> 02:05:46.391
<i>and has slapped it away
several times.</i>

02:05:50.533 --> 02:05:53.593
Keep moving, boy-o!
You stay with him!

02:05:54.203 --> 02:05:55.534
Son of a bitch!

02:05:56.139 --> 02:05:59.108
<i>Braddock with a shoeshine.
Left, right!</i>

02:05:59.442 --> 02:06:01.569
Am I seeing what I'm seeing?

02:06:01.844 --> 02:06:03.778
Finish him, Jimmy. Finish him!

02:06:03.846 --> 02:06:05.837
Braddock, Braddock!

02:06:15.024 --> 02:06:17.891
<i>Maxie's glamour-boy smile
is now a bloody grimace.</i>

02:06:19.262 --> 02:06:22.129
<i>This crowd is desperately
hoping for a Braddock victory.</i>

02:06:22.198 --> 02:06:25.361
<i>But Mr. Baer might have something to say
about that.</i>

02:06:28.738 --> 02:06:30.069
Holy crap!

02:06:36.345 --> 02:06:37.573
Low blow!

02:06:37.647 --> 02:06:39.842
That last low blow
will cost you the round, Max.

02:06:39.916 --> 02:06:41.679
Jesus!
It'll cost you the round.

02:06:43.486 --> 02:06:45.545
Why don't you just kick him
in the balls, huh?

02:06:45.621 --> 02:06:46.610
Joe, back in your corner!

02:06:46.689 --> 02:06:48.816
What are you afraid of,
you son of a bitch?

02:06:48.891 --> 02:06:50.222
Get back to your corner!

02:06:52.962 --> 02:06:54.452
Come on, Ref!

02:06:55.932 --> 02:06:59.197
<i>McAvoy is on the verge of
losing control of this fight.</i>

02:07:03.573 --> 02:07:05.666
Knock him on the ground, Bulldog!

02:07:08.144 --> 02:07:10.112
Last round.
That's right! Next champ!

02:07:10.179 --> 02:07:12.044
You better worry about Baer's
corner in this next round.

02:07:12.114 --> 02:07:13.308
You know what I mean.

02:07:13.382 --> 02:07:16.078
You won this one.
It's a cinch. It is yours.

02:07:17.353 --> 02:07:20.322
But I want you to play it
cagey now. All right?

02:07:20.623 --> 02:07:22.386
I know you don't like
laying back

02:07:22.458 --> 02:07:24.585
but I want you to stay away
from his right

02:07:24.660 --> 02:07:26.753
do you understand me?
Stay away.

02:07:27.129 --> 02:07:28.426
Right hand.

02:07:28.664 --> 02:07:31.861
You're behind.
Are you listening to me?

02:07:31.934 --> 02:07:35.131
You want to lose the championship
to this goddamn nobody?

02:07:35.404 --> 02:07:36.769
Hey. Come on, Jimmy!

02:07:36.839 --> 02:07:38.170
This is your night.

02:07:40.610 --> 02:07:42.601
Stay away. Put him down!

02:07:44.580 --> 02:07:46.878
Use your right hand.
Right hand.

02:07:52.421 --> 02:07:55.390
Ten seconds!
Come on now. Finish him.

02:07:59.295 --> 02:08:02.287
It's the last round,
Jimmy. There ain't no more.

02:08:02.932 --> 02:08:06.732
You play this bastard smart
and they can't take it from you!

02:08:16.112 --> 02:08:17.943
<i>One more round to go, folks.</i>

02:08:18.080 --> 02:08:19.775
<i>McAvoy stands
at center ring</i>

02:08:19.849 --> 02:08:22.044
<i>waiting for the fighters
to join him.</i>

02:08:43.472 --> 02:08:44.905
Touch gloves.

02:08:47.209 --> 02:08:49.200
<i>The boys touch gloves
at center ring.</i>

02:08:50.179 --> 02:08:51.476
<i>And now they're right
back at it.</i>

02:08:51.547 --> 02:08:52.809
Oh, no, Jimmy!

02:08:55.318 --> 02:08:56.683
Leave him alone!

02:08:58.287 --> 02:09:00.016
Stay away from him!

02:09:00.456 --> 02:09:01.946
That ain't laying back!

02:09:02.024 --> 02:09:03.924
<i>Braddock's corner
is yelling at Braddock</i>

02:09:03.993 --> 02:09:05.255
<i>to stay away from Baer.</i>

02:09:05.328 --> 02:09:07.125
<i>Because Baer is looking
for the knockout.</i>

02:09:07.196 --> 02:09:09.096
Stay off him, Jim. Come on!

02:09:11.901 --> 02:09:13.732
Right hand, Max. Yes!

02:09:21.544 --> 02:09:23.011
What is he, stupid?

02:09:26.248 --> 02:09:28.148
Step away!

02:09:28.317 --> 02:09:30.877
<i>Braddock trying to survive
this brutal onslaught!</i>

02:09:30.953 --> 02:09:32.648
Stay off him!

02:09:33.556 --> 02:09:35.490
Don't let him touch you!

02:09:35.558 --> 02:09:37.583
Hey, looking good, Maxie!

02:09:42.164 --> 02:09:44.928
Watch the uppercut! Just
stay the hell away from him!

02:09:45.000 --> 02:09:47.628
<i>Baer cutting loose
with thunderous shots.</i>

02:09:47.703 --> 02:09:48.931
<i>A left to the body.</i>

02:09:49.004 --> 02:09:50.562
<i>Baer again with a right!</i>

02:09:50.639 --> 02:09:53.767
<i>Braddock covering up,
trying to hang on.</i>

02:09:54.243 --> 02:09:55.608
<i>Baer looking for the knockout.</i>

02:09:55.678 --> 02:09:58.374
<i>He doesn't want this one
to go to the cards, folks.</i>

02:09:58.447 --> 02:10:00.711
<i>They pound each other
with lefts and rights.</i>

02:10:00.783 --> 02:10:02.876
<i>Braddock blocking
with his gloves and elbows.</i>

02:10:02.952 --> 02:10:05.546
<i>Snaps a big right
to Maxie's jaw!</i>

02:10:14.864 --> 02:10:17.264
<i>Baer smashes him
with a big right!</i>

02:10:25.508 --> 02:10:27.738
<i>Braddock is back on the ropes.</i>

02:11:14.190 --> 02:11:16.522
<i>Braddock lands
a crushing right.</i>

02:11:17.293 --> 02:11:19.591
<i>Maxie desperately wants
to keep the crown</i>

02:11:19.662 --> 02:11:21.129
<i>from slipping away.</i>

02:11:24.633 --> 02:11:26.464
Jesus Christ.

02:11:32.174 --> 02:11:33.505
Stay with him!

02:11:38.314 --> 02:11:40.282
<i>Both fighters are tired.</i>

02:11:50.059 --> 02:11:52.459
<i>Baer is trying wildly
for the knockout!</i>

02:11:52.761 --> 02:11:54.194
<i>But Jimmy is still standing</i>

02:11:54.263 --> 02:11:57.027
<i>and he's not only standing,
he's moving forward.</i>

02:12:09.411 --> 02:12:12.676
<i>This is the finish.
Both boys are tired.</i>

02:12:12.915 --> 02:12:16.373
<i>This is not boxing, folks.
This is a walloping ballet.</i>

02:12:21.056 --> 02:12:22.353
Ten seconds!

02:12:22.424 --> 02:12:24.415
Time's up!
Son of a bitch.

02:12:38.274 --> 02:12:41.368
<i>That is the bell! It's over!
This fight is over!</i>

02:12:43.512 --> 02:12:45.036
Son of a bitch!

02:12:52.788 --> 02:12:55.450
<i>What a fight! Unbelievable!</i>

02:12:59.628 --> 02:13:00.720
<i>Braddock came
into this fight</i>

02:13:00.796 --> 02:13:02.559
<i>the biggest underdog
Come on, sweetheart.</i>

02:13:02.631 --> 02:13:04.030
<i>in pugilistic history.
You did it!</i>

02:13:04.099 --> 02:13:06.431
<i>For 15 rounds he gave it everything
he had</i>

02:13:06.502 --> 02:13:08.834
<i>against the younger,
stronger champion.</i>

02:13:20.182 --> 02:13:22.207
<i>We are waiting
for the decision.</i>

02:13:23.419 --> 02:13:24.943
Mae, it's all right.

02:13:30.426 --> 02:13:31.893
Hey, McAvoy!

02:13:33.662 --> 02:13:35.596
What?
Help me out here. Help me out.

02:13:35.664 --> 02:13:38.497
How did you score the fight?
Nine-five, one even.

02:13:39.068 --> 02:13:40.035
Which way?

02:13:40.102 --> 02:13:41.899
You'll have to read it
in the papers, Sporty.

02:13:41.971 --> 02:13:43.165
Oh, come on!

02:13:46.141 --> 02:13:48.006
What the hell is this crap?

02:13:51.280 --> 02:13:53.840
I'll tell you this much, they take
this long to make a decision

02:13:53.916 --> 02:13:56.248
they're gonna decide
to screw somebody.

02:13:57.186 --> 02:13:58.585
Make a decision.

02:13:58.721 --> 02:14:00.746
They're gonna rob
this poor bastard.

02:14:00.823 --> 02:14:02.984
Unbelievable bullshit.
You win it.

02:14:09.531 --> 02:14:13.297
Come on, make a decision!
Tell us who won, come on!

02:14:15.904 --> 02:14:18.600
<i>The crowd, on its feet
for almost the entire fight</i>

02:14:18.674 --> 02:14:21.666
<i>is still standing, yelling for who
they clearly believe</i>

02:14:21.744 --> 02:14:23.939
<i>to be the winner of
this fight.</i>

02:14:25.547 --> 02:14:28.744
<i>But they'll have to wait
and see how the judges scored it.</i>

02:14:46.402 --> 02:14:48.529
<i>Ladies and gentlemen</i>

02:14:49.271 --> 02:14:51.296
<i>we have your decision.</i>

02:14:53.008 --> 02:14:54.771
<i>It's unanimous!</i>

02:14:55.110 --> 02:14:59.604
<i>Winner, and the new world
heavyweight champion</i>

02:15:01.116 --> 02:15:03.243
<i>James J. Braddock!</i>

02:15:20.069 --> 02:15:21.502
You son of a bitch.

02:15:22.104 --> 02:15:24.664
<i>James Braddock
has defeated Max Baer</i>

02:15:24.740 --> 02:15:27.538
<i>for the heavyweight
championship of the world!</i>

02:15:29.111 --> 02:15:31.170
He won!

02:15:48.630 --> 02:15:50.291
You earned it.
Hell of a fight.
